N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 113.20 - Expedited procedure

State Regulations

If the appeal board determines that an appeal requires
expeditious determination, it may by filing an order direct that the time
requirements set forth in these regulations be shortened as set forth in such
order. Notes
